    <name>ISW Controller</name>
    <summary>Control ISW systems</summary>
    <description>
        <p>See what's playing and add your own songs, play sounds from the soundboard, control the airconditioner and buy stuff in the shop.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Control the media player, airconditioner and shop, right from your desktop</li>
            <li>Stays out of your way by always sticking to the desktop</li>
            <li>Move the window by dragging any part of it</li>
            <li>Quit with the handy shortcut Ctrl + Q</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
    <provides>
        <binary>com.github.tuurdutoit.elementary-isw-controller</binary>
    </provides>
    <screenshots>
        <screenshot type="default">
            <image>https://raw.githubusercontent.com/tuurdutoit/elementary-isw-controller/master/data/screenshot.png</image>
